# BehaviorCI runtime data.
# In *your* project you may choose to commit .behaviorci/behaviorci.db so that
# baselines travel with the repo (see the "Team workflows" docs). In this
# repository the database is only a transient self-test artifact, so we ignore
# the whole directory.
.behaviorci/

